OL,7,FResponding to the attack, the POA said
OL,8,Ftheir thoughts were with the officers
OL,9,Fand their families, adding: "No
OL,10,FOfficer should be subject to cowardly
OL,11,Fand vicious attacks at work.
OL,13,F"This attack displays the dangers
OL,14,Fbrave prison officers face on a daily
OL,15,Fbasis.
OL,17,F"Things have to change."
OL,19,FAbedi was jailed for life in August
OL,20,F2020 and is currently serving at the
OL,21,Fcategory A HMP Frankland.
