OL,7,FCategory A is the highest level of
OL,8,Fsecurity, housing some of the
OL,9,Fcountry's most serious criminals.
OL,11,FFrankland also has a separation centre.
OL,13,FThese centres, introduced in 2017, aim
OL,14,Fto control prisoners with extreme
OL,15,Fviews, for example by preventing them
OL,16,Ffrom disrupting the prison estate,
OL,17,Fsupporting acts of terrorism or
OL,18,Fradicalising other inmates.
