OL,7,FPOA's national chairman, Mark
OL,8,FFairhurst, told Sky News: "This attack
OL,9,Fwas actually in a separation centre,
OL,10,Fat Frankland, which houses the most
OL,11,Fdangerous criminals that society
OL,12,Fthrows at us.
OL,14,F"And part of the normal regime is to
OL,15,Fallow prisoners in that separation
OL,16,Fcentre to cook their own meals.
