OL,7,F"So this individual has been heating
OL,8,Fup cooking oil, has subdued the staff
OL,9,Fby throwing it over them, and then has
OL,10,Fproceeded to stab and slash them with
OL,11,Fa improvised weapon."
OL,13,FMr Fairhurt also called for the
OL,14,Fremoval of cooking areas from
OL,15,Fseparation facilities to reduce the
OL,16,Fthreat from prison officers.
