OL,7,FIt said the Frankland unit was on a
OL,8,Fnarrow corridor with a small "room for
OL,9,Fassociation" and an area for prisoners
OL,10,Fto cook and prepare food.
OL,12,FThere were no facilities on the wing
OL,13,Fand staff could arrange for prisoners
OL,14,Fto visit the main prison gym or to be
OL,15,Ftaken off the unit for education, the
OL,16,Freport said.
